def date_time():
    time = datetime.datetime.now()
    hr = time.strftime("%I")
    min= time.strftime("%M")
    sec= time.strftime("%S")
    am= time.strftime("%p")
    # for date
    date= time.strftime("%d")
    mon= time.strftime("%m")
    year= time.strftime("%y")
